title: Topic 001 Question 019
body: You have a Fabric workspace named Workspace1 that contains a dataflow named Dataflow1. Dataflow1 has a query that returns 2,000 rows.
You view the query in Power Query as shown in the following exhibit.
What can you identify about the pickupLongitude column?
options: All the table rows are profiled.
There are 935 values that occur only once.
